			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">How to Love an Oyster</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">The Pacific coast’s only native oyster is making a comeback, but it still needs a little help from its friends.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/brendan-borrell/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Brendan Borrell</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
